This Dark Jedi has scant offensive or defensive Force powers but is unequaled in the art of combat with two lightsabers.

^2Weaponry:
- Dual Lightsabers
-- Saber Defense 3
--- 20% less Dmg

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Push (2)
- Pull (2)

^8Attributes:
- Cortosis (1)
- Force Block/Focus (2)
- Bunny Hop (1)
- Slow Faller
- BP Free Jumps
- 1 Extra Life
"